# CODEOWNERS — https://docs.github.com/articles/about-code-owners
#
# Scoped to production code and tests only. PRs touching these paths require
# a review from a listed owner before merge (enforced via
# `require_code_owner_reviews` on the `main` branch protection rule).
#
# Other paths (docs, .assets, build orchestrator, CI workflows, root config,
# changelogs, etc.) have no code owner and are gated only by the required CI
# status check.

/src/**     @Fallout-build/maintainers
/tests/**   @Fallout-build/maintainers
